Summary 
All major features were successfully tested with the Dockerized MySQL database. The system now supports persistent storage for parking lots and reservations, ensuring that all data remains consistent across backend restarts and Docker container restarts. 
This testing confirms that SmartPark has transitioned from an in-memory system to a fully persistent, database-backed application with reliable data integrity and full-stack functionality. 
